00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:29.880
Ya, aku akan bersamamu
di atas panggung, sungguh.

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:31.960
Mengerti?  - Ya.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:35.920
Ayo pergi..
- Ya, ayo pergi..

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:38.160
Ayah..

